flowchart LR
  SysTick[SysTick_Handler] --> tick[tick wake timers]
  tick --> slice[time slice check]
  slice --> pend[PendSV pend]
  pend --> PendSV[PendSV_Handler]
  PendSV --> save[save R4-R11 on PSP]
  save --> sched[scheduler_get_next]
  sched --> restore[restore R4-R11 PSP]
  restore --> ret[exception return to task]
